cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this analysis corpus, please cite it as below."
title: "Model Personality Corpus"
abstract: >
  An analysis corpus of model-personality substrates derived from the
  Convergent Form, Divergent Voice II raw trace corpus. Includes per-sample
  freeflow personality/vibe readings, per-model personality profiles and cards,
  values-probe summaries, taxonomy tables, route/provider difference reports,
  and methodology notes for studying model posture across frontier LLMs.
